  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dc0 \u0d85\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0d82\u0dc1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d91\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A new ministry is coming",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A new Ministry as the Ministry of Technology has been gazetted. President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa has published this Ministry in a Gazette Notification",
        "Dhammika Perera was sworn in as the new Minister of Technology and Investment Promotion.",
        "Accordingly, the Ministry of Technology has been published in a separate gazette notification and is currently under the President."
      ],
